@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_jrizoq(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (((tmp + 0.07 - v1 + 0.26) / v1) * wp.sin((v2 + 0.19 + v0 + 0.40)))
    v2 = tmp
    tmp = wp.exp((0.94 - (tmp + 0.98 + v1 + 0.38)))
    v1 = wp.cos(wp.abs(wp.cos(v0 + 0.29)))
    tmp = wp.cos((wp.abs(v1 + 0.58) * v2))
    data[tid] = v0
